summary: A enthusiastic professional who is able to maintain a good balance between the interests of the employee (s) and the importance of the organization. That also  try’s, from a personal aproach and with empathy, to offer a certain perspective and confidence so that a sustainable and future-proof solution is achieved. Aware of the importance of advice and support with a good absenteeism policy.
